{"tid":1926743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台高質記錄片:奪命流感5000萬，每一個香港人都應該要睇，特別係d鬆懈個d人","createTime":"2020-03-15T10:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T06:02:28.000Z","uid":36901,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c8f5b5d5f2a650c0bc72e68cc105a44c793cba","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:14:37.000Z","msg":"而家有得網上睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thefluthatkilled50million/episode/625787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fthefluthatkilled50million%2Fepisode%2F625787&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=cc55ec14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thefluthatkilled50million/episode/625787</a><br />\n<br />\n1918年，第一次世界大戰結束。數以百萬計的人死亡，世界因戰爭而筋疲力盡。可惜不消多久，新一輪的恐慌席捲全球，一種可怕的病毒出現，殺死了超過五千萬人，這就是西班牙流感。這紀錄片透過個案重組與及目擊者，包括科學家、醫護人員、軍人、普羅市民和政客的親身經歷，再一次將昔日的慘況呈現觀眾眼前，讓大家了解當年人類如何面對病毒的襲擊和尋找治療的方法。一個世紀後的今天，希望人類藉此歷史吸取教訓，有助大家應對未來全球流感的大爆發。"},{"pid":"c66187cd649a322d18c4b721cfa73f13f56bd557","tid":1926743,"uid":276693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"p牌無得推"},{"pid":"f720cf9fc9998a7fe1fb83f38289957a77d90934","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"而家武漢肺炎根本係走緊西班牙流感條路<br />\n不過武肺傳播速度更快<br />\n西班牙流感開頭都好似唔是好勁<br />\n直到秋天爆第二波就死得好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家個d可能只係前菜"},{"pid":"469cfd6bd0af1671c630a48370b45529b9d41210","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Spanish_flu_death_chart.png/300px-Spanish_flu_death_chart.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe2%2FSpanish_flu_death_chart.png%2F300px-Spanish_flu_death_chart.png&h=8bc19c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙流感最致命係第二波<br />\n秋天一變種就黎料<br />\n好似瘟疫公司咁"},{"pid":"96226b58f282c30a074bb250c9c7282c3733140e","tid":1926743,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"睇曬了丶<br />\n我老母剩係睇嗰日驚😅"},{"pid":"4bf0f05a7e37f610165535bd53236d2861eda955","tid":1926743,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2042e071c11b5b51335d1ba486692ae7b24a419","tid":1926743,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6d26cfcfe3c50f8569aa3816842b045dbc9cb1c","tid":1926743,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"2bfc073b5b051381e45f632f469cca3c1d310929","tid":1926743,"uid":268181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24cdf7d8665c1f9b448d398a0ba8015a31423451","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cf9e7b5c1a1130216c7b9875c8bfc0d99f79c26","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4de2fbca07a4688cdc055a5d2d575cf5aea32a19","tid":1926743,"uid":88363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"睇完好心寒<br />\n同而家武肺發展既進展勁似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75189e1cf7cb299f78a8baeb3567aaf1b1648ef6","tid":1926743,"uid":294413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"我想去異世界好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5df4be2bb793ca387e57f2bde7187d27a9e4bf7","tid":1926743,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:28:42.000Z","msg":